#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.271:0.2"
msgid "27. Kammapathavagga "
msgstr "27. Ways of Performing Deeds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.271:0.3"
msgid "271. Abhijjhālusutta "
msgstr "271. Covetousness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.271:1.1"
msgid "… pe … Attanā ca abhijjhālu hoti, parañca abhijjhāya samādapeti, abhijjhāya ca samanuñño hoti, abhijjhāya ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati … pe …. "
msgstr "… They themselves are covetous … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.271:2.1"
msgid "Attanā ca anabhijjhālu hoti, parañca anabhijjhāya samādapeti, anabhijjhāya ca samanuñño hoti, anabhijjhāya ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—imehi kho … pe …. "
msgstr "… They themselves are content … "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.271:2.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

